    "body": "This unintended big scroll bars appear in Windows and Electron 1.5 when DPI scale is large.\r\n\r\nHow to reproduce:\r\n\r\n* Set display DPI scale to 200% in Windows and relogin\r\n* Open webpage with scrollbar in Electron (e.g., Electron tests)\r\n* The big scroll bar appears\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1025246/22318136/9207caf0-e3bb-11e6-8405-c2d85e839e32.png)\r\n"
